          <p>Honestly: you'll notice more hydrated, radiant skin from the 1st or 2nd session — the immediate effect of deep heat. The firming effect settles between sessions 5 and 8, when collagen reorganises. The consolidated result shows after all 10 sessions, with progressive improvement for another 3 to 6 months as your skin keeps regenerating. If anyone promises faster than that, they're selling hype.</p>
